                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-221-off1158 t18320705-221-crimeloc1161"></join>. On the 14th of June I was in the shop, and missed a silk handkerchief, which had been pinned up at the door, and I had seen safe not more than five minutes before; I received information, and ran up Magpie-alley - I saw the prisoner running up Blossom-street; I pursued, and took him in Gun-street; I said,"I want you, you took a handkerchief from our door;" he gave me this handkerchief, and said he had picked it up.</p>
