               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw it at the corner of Magpie-alley - I took it up; a woman said it belonged to a boy she saw running, and I ran on.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a very good character.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 17.</p>
